{{Top|leg}}
'''Abesmi''' was an "island-monolith"<ref name="Unknown Soldier">{{InsiderCite|86|Unknown Soldier: The Story of General Grievous}}</ref> located in the [[Jenuwaa Sea]] on [[Kalee/Legends|Kalee]]. It was believed to be the point from which the native [[Deity/Legends|gods]] ascended to heaven. The native [[Kaleesh/Legends|Kaleesh]] [[Species/Legends|species]] took it to be a sacred place, and it was an important altar of worship.<ref name="TNEGAS">''[[The New Essential Guide to Alien Species]]''</ref>

After the [[Death/Legends|death]] of [[Ronderu lij Kummar]], [[Grievous/Legends|Qymaen jai Sheelal]] traveled across the [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]] to Abesmi to beg the [[God/Legends|gods]] to raise her from the sea that had claimed her body so that he might see her one last time. His prayers were to no avail.<ref name="Unknown Soldier" />

